Name: Audi Q2
Description: Audi Q2. Audi Q2 is a 5 seater SUV available in a price range of ₹ 35.00 - 48.90 Lakh. It is available in 6 variants, 1984 cc engine option and 1 transmission.

Name: Audi A4
Description: Audi A4 price starts at ₹ 43.06 Lakh and goes upto ₹ 50.99 Lakh (Avg. ex-showroom). A4 comes in 3 variants. A4 top model price in petrol is ₹ 50.99 Lakh.

Name: Audi Q7
Description: Audi Q7 is a 7 seater SUV available in a price range of Rs. 83.32 - 88.98 Lakh*. It is available in 2 variants, a 2995 cc, BS6.

Name: BMW 3 Series
Description: The seventh-generation BMW 3 Series was launched in India back in August 2019. The model is currently available in four trims that include 330i Sport, 320d Luxury Edition, 330i M Sport, and the M340i xDrive.

Name: BMW X1
Description: The BMW X1 is available in four trim levels, namely the X1 sDrive20i SportX, sDrive20i xLine, sDrive20d xLine and sDrive20i Tech Edition.

Name: BMW Z4
Description: The updated BMW Z4 was launched in India on 08 April 2019.

Name: Rolls-Royce Dawn
Description: Rolls-Royce Dawn price is ₹ 6.99 Crore (on-road Mumbai). Dawn comes in 1 variant. Dawn top model price in petrol is ₹ 6.99 Crore. Whereas the price of Dawn automatic version starts from ₹ 6.99 Crore.

Name: Rolls-Royce Phantom VIII
Description: The Rolls-Royce Phantom VIII was launched in India on 23 February 2018. This is the current flagship model made by Rolls-Royce Motor Cars.

Name: Rolls-Royce Cullinan
Description: Rolls-Royce Cullinan price is ₹ 8.20 Crore (on-road Mumbai). Cullinan comes in 1 variant. Cullinan top model price in petrol is ₹ 8.20 Crore. Whereas the price of Cullinan automatic version starts from ₹ 8.20 Crore.
